data.description: OAK PARK~ PRISTINE Paradise! Star Studded lighting and pavers offer amazing curb appeal! CBS - Fully remodeled from floor to ceiling! 3 Bd/ 1 Ba / Carport. Open Concept. Bright and cheery! Crown molding. Shaker cabinets, SS appliances. 8x12 Utility room (Could be 2nd Bath). Triple paver driveway (boat parking), lighted columns and MBox. New - Stucco exterior and paint. 14x16 Workshop. Professional landscaping and irrigation. 12X24 Covered patio and Spacious open patio for entertaining with fire pit. Fenced, lush lawn and graceful trees. SENSATIONAL EXCELLENCE! Dimensions are approximate, must measure for exact.
